Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:07.26,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Alone 光と闇の Horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:12.78,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}I was Born 泣きながら 生まれてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:17.99,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Why not 闘い得た　絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:26.62,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Just now　この手の中で　熱く輝け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.30,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}One in a seven billion の憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:44.86,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Someday 世界が終わる日が　来たって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:50.06,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}So，What？　1ミリの悔いもない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:55.78,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Say， yeah！！　一筋に走る流れ星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.44,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}鼓動ドキドキ止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:03.19,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}迷いも全部　蹴っ飛ばせ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:08.71,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}宇宙に　抱かれし　蒼い地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:13.98,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}いつも心に描く　エリシオン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:19.34,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}過去も未来も　自分が創る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:24.60,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}永遠の“Stellar”を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:30.07,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}“命のうた”が聞こえる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:08.06,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義の剣は折れ 無機質に転がった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:13.43,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支えてた自分 reasonとか 見えなくなってしまうの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:18.60,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手で掴んでも 右手からこぼれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:23.69,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣いてなんかいないのに 霞んで行く情景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:28.98,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ゆらり揺れて 惑わす世界はきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:33.44,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来切符を探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:39.49,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈍い音に 焦らされるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:43.67,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走り出さなきゃ ゴールはない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:49.99,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,future is serious! future is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:55.40,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんで、どうして、心が邪魔をするの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.77,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,future is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:07.18,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何十回繰り返しても 戸惑いを振り払って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:17.26,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がる まだ夢を見たまま…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,bt,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)}第5話 「蓋諾斯城的{\1c&537ea3&}秘{\1c&HFFFFFF&}密」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審問官大人 是否聽說了剛剛發佈的告示？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說 女王發佈了圍剿叛亂者的通緝令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將擾亂大陸秩序的叛亂者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是以安妮洛特為首的賊黨一舉殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是女王的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以斯琪大人 女王需要你助我們一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是個侍奉上帝的審問官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取締叛亂者並不是我的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有女王的命令你也要拒絕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所遵從的惟有上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信仰上帝的話就更必須協助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此話怎講
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛亂者安妮洛特體內流淌著惡魔之血
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:00:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即為異端者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流淌著…惡魔之血？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:36.39,bt,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)}第9話 「武士{\1c&3e6f53&}登{\1c&HFFFFFF&}場」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猩猩果然就該待在籠子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道麼 殲滅美鬥士的行動開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殲的就是你這種反抗姐姐大人的鬥士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:03:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人可是叫我一個不剩通通殺光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗娜 你還是這麼笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不明白自己的處境麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影戰士·瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的表情應該是聽過這名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各地反抗姐姐大人胡作非為的神秘鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你知道她的真實身份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說 麗斯蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不說讓你吃不了兜著走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近缺乏刺激 讓我心裡發癢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來戰個痛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 我們覺得餓的速度是不是太快了點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從離開了夫人 怎麼吃都吃不飽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊 我去找點趁手的食材算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人 速速現身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙拿著劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是女王的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我並不是女王的士兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快喊小泉來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天在呼喚 地在呼喚 人們在呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除惡的使命在呼喚我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰神武士·泉登場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的走狗 我泉不允許你再為非作歹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快和我堂堂正正地戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那劍是擺設嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺設…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對現在的我來說或許是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用打就投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 不愧是小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 原來不是女王的士兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算是真正的士兵來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小泉在 瞬間就能幹翻她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這村裡只有小孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不過現在有小泉在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算壞蛋士兵來了也不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞蛋士兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是女王的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常來這附近的村莊搞破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的士兵竟然對這種村莊出手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王軍的魔爪竟然伸到這種小村莊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底打著什麼算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我是說 剛才為什麼收了劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為覺得我太弱而不肯出手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人一開始就是強大的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不斷鍛煉誰都能變強大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去鍛煉也會變強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 就是那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你樂意的話 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你教我劍術也…也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說要是你無論如何都想教的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我學一下也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是想讓我教你劍術嗎 就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是我來當你徒弟也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你應該有收徒弟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒弟嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們應該不算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他們約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保護這些孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只能依靠我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這種情況下你還要見死不救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻太幼稚 20分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…那是什麼分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經教過我武功的人的口頭禪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最後也沒能拿到100分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到我來教了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌棄的話 讓我幫助你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你說到這份上我就姑且同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材嬌小的人 不要用蠻力進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活用速度 精確打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:07:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腋下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二擊就到眉心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算力道不夠 只要打擊準確
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能打倒敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 如果能做到那樣能得100分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味在意分數 可是永遠都不會長進的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你既然這麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是可以把女王的軍隊全部消滅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地不是起叛亂嗎 安妮洛特也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話太多 20分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 安妮洛特 我跟你說了多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭要抬高看著遠方 12分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰沒有使勁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 她要搶我在森林裡找到的小熊玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想抱小熊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我找到的小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小熊要是聽到你們吵架會怎麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小熊傷心了又回到森林裡怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真乖 100分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先給你抱也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了河邊就換你抱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這裡只有小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人們都被捲進戰亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下孩子們互相幫助耕種田地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強度過難關
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而最近被女王的士兵盯上了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人朝著村子來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女王的士兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 獨自一人還帶著劍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天在呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地在呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們在呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除惡的使命在呼喚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影戰士·瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 瑪麗亞 今天和我一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 瑪麗亞要和我一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那大家一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞 我聽過你的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大陸每個角落揭起反旗與女王戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神出鬼沒的你 被人們稱為幻影戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼時候變得那麼出名了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何止是有名 在上一屆女皇之刃還奪得了冠…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 這件事可是秘密別隨便亂說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥 啥都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這位著名的瑪麗亞為什麼會來村裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞是這個村子的恩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有大人而陷入困境的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她教會了我們很多東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣為什麼又丟下村子一走了之了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她可是流浪戰士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納…納尼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞總是一下就睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 這就要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能一直留在這裡打擾你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的劍術你也還沒有教完
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況現在瑪麗亞也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王軍的野營地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒有吃得這麼飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心把貝爾菲那份也吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔物？ 貝爾菲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它還有同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在泉的村子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種忍耐到極限的點到即止感還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然小孩子也難以割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這位小姐也非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要努力 也能保護大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就知道瑪麗亞 瑪麗亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞有什麼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耐性不夠 再也忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔 魔物？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我吃個一乾二淨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞 快去把瑪麗亞叫起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 瑪麗亞一睡著就喊不醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那房子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 今天大家都來這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽好 快藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 和女王的士兵不是一個級別
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞還在睡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能保護這個村子 能保護孩子們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟夫人有著同樣的香氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 大家別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是極品食材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新鮮程度真讓人按捺不住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 意外地頑強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉

Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下總算能盡情享用了 那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也忍不住了 不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉 挺住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不放棄 因為和大家約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是戰神武士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉 跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腋下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眉心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了結你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說過砧板上的鯉魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吃的時候可要老實點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯉魚躍過龍門化身為龍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神龍擺尾(Dragon Tail)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞 謝謝你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:19:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在夢中也聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的呼喊 成為了大家的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是「有志者 事竟成」的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來還想在這裡多待會的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特你就為更多的人而努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這村子絕對會由我和大家保護好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 有你在我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉 大家就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「有志者 事竟成」…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必彷徨 不再躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會與心中的志向一同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開拓嶄新的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪都不會去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起改變這片大陸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/ed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區那種滑稽的玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其 其實我一個人也完全能對付
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.49,0:23:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞和安妮洛特姐姐大人也挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.02,0:23:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？下次是天使要來？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 天使與陷阱與女王的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要是讓我碰到女王軍 一定打她們個落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我可是真正的武士
